trans-unit.source: Used in conjunction with the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveCompleted"></xref> event, which is signaled when a resolve request for a specific <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName"></xref> has completed.
trans-unit.target: Brukes sammen med den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveCompleted"> </xref> som angis når en løs forespørsel om en bestemt <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName"> </xref> er fullført.

trans-unit.source: To use the ResolveCompletedEventArgs object, instantiate a <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver> object and utilize one of the Resolve methods.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil bruke ResolveCompletedEventArgs-objekt, kan du starte en <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver>objekt og bruke én av metodene Løs.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver>

trans-unit.source: For asynchronous processing, use the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync%2A> method.

When the Resolver has reached the end of the Cloud(s) to query for the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName>, or it has reached the maximum number of record entries for the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecordCollection> it is constructing, the event to complete the resolve process is raised, and the associated delegate causes ResolveAsync to complete.
trans-unit.target: Når av løseren har nådd slutten av Cloud(s) for spørring etter den <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName>, eller den har nådd det maksimale antallet registrere poster for den <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecordCollection>det er å lage hendelsen for å fullføre prosessen Løs oppstår og tilknyttede representanten fører til at ResolveAsync skal fullføres.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecordCollection> </xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName>

trans-unit.source: The event can also be raised for abnormal completions, which do not return a collection.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsen kan også oppstå for unormal fullføres, som ikke returnerer en samling.

trans-unit.source: This event is raised only once when all endpoints have been found.
trans-unit.target: Denne hendelsen oppstår når når alle endepunkt er funnet.

trans-unit.source: All references to this instance of the Resolver object are coordinated with a supplied token, which is a unique, developer-determined identifier for this asynchronous resolve request.
trans-unit.target: Alle referanser til denne forekomsten av Løsningsprogrammet-objektet er koordinert med angitt token, som er en unik, developer fastsettes identifikator for denne asynkrone Løs-forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.ResolveCompletedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.ResolveCompletedEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The collection associated with the peer name that was resolved.
Returns an exception if an error occurred.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et unntak hvis det oppstod en feilen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*> operation was cancelled, otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*>operasjonen ble avbrutt, ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*>

trans-unit.source: The user token specified when a <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*> operation was started.

trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecordCollection"> </xref> objekt til å løse.

trans-unit.source: This event is raised when all clouds have been queried for this peer name, or when the maximum number of peer name records has been retrieved.
trans-unit.target: Denne hendelsen oppstår når alle skyer har blitt forespurt for denne nodenavn, eller når maksimalt antall poster for node-navnet er hentet.

trans-unit.source: It is raised by putting the peer name record collection into the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.ResolveCompletedEventArgs> event argument for which the OnResolveCompleted method is waiting.
trans-unit.target: Det oppstår ved å sette inn peer name registrere samlingen i den <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.ResolveCompletedEventArgs>hendelsen argumentet metoden OnResolveCompleted venter.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.ResolveCompletedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The change in state awakens the process.
Unless explicitly specified, the default value for all properties is `null` for reference types and zero (0) for properties of type `int`.
trans-unit.target: Med mindre du eksplisitt angitt, er standardverdien for alle egenskaper `null` for referansetyper og null (0) for egenskaper av typen `int`.

trans-unit.source: If no records were found, `null` is returned.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen oppføringer ble funnet, `null` returneres.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecordCollection"></xref> object to resolve is the one found in response to a <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*> operation on a specific <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameRecordCollection"> </xref> objekt til å løse er funnet i svaret på en <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*>operasjon på en bestemt <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerName"> </xref>.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.PeerNameResolver.ResolveAsync*>
